{"word":"G121 - ἄθωος - áthōos - ath'-o-os - Innocent","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄθωος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">áthōos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ath'-o-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Innocent</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"குற்றமில்லாத, குற்றமற்ற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"unpunished, innocent"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a probable derivative of <a href=\"#/G5087 - τίθημι - títhēmi - tith'-ay-mee/5087\">G5087</a> (meaning a <i>penalty</i>); <i>not guilty:</i> - innocent.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}